Baseline mix (kg/m3): {"cement": 320, "slag": 0, "sand": 780, "chips": 1000, "water": 160}
Request: Replace about 20% of the cement with slag.
Return only the new mix as JSON with the same keys.

Baseline mix (kg/m3): {"cement": 320, "slag": 0, "sand": 780, "chips": 1000, "water": 160}
Request: Cut cement by 60 and swap 50 of the sand over to chips.
Return only the new mix as JSON with the same keys.

Baseline mix (kg/m3): {"cement": 300, "slag": 0, "sand": 800, "chips": 950, "water": 150}
Request: Replace a third of the cement with slag and drop the water by 5.
Return only the new mix as JSON with the same keys.

Baseline mix (kg/m3): {"cement": 320, "slag": 0, "sand": 780, "chips": 1000, "water": 160}
Request: Bump the water down by 10 and add 40 kg of slag.
Return only the new mix as JSON with the same keys.

Baseline mix (kg/m3): {"cement": 280, "slag": 40, "sand": 760, "chips": 1020, "water": 158}
Request: Take 30 kg out of the cement and put it into slag.
Return only the new mix as JSON with the same keys.
